"title": "7950: mission, of Jesus Christ",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7950: mission, of jesus christ",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ came to reveal God, to announce the coming of God's kingdom and to redeem a fallen humanity through his death on the cross. Though he came first to the Jews, the scope of Christ's mission includes the whole human race and continues through the Spirit-empowered witness of the church.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mission originated with God</h2>\n<h3>It was purposed by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18-1Pet1:20\">1PE 1:18–1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4-Eph1:5\">EPH 1:4–1:5</a></p>\n<h3>The Father sent the Son</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4-Gal4:5\">GAL 4:4–4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:37-John5:38\">JHN 5:37–5:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:29\">JHN 7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:42\">JHN 8:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:36\">JHN 10:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:8\">JHN 17:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:14\">1JN 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ came in willing obedience to the Father</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:38\">JHN 6:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:5-Phil2:8\">PHP 2:5–2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's mission was motivated by God's love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8\">ROM 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:10\">1JN 4:10</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mission was to make God known</h2>\n<h3>He reveals God in his own person</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:18\">JHN 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9\">JHN 14:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:26\">JHN 17:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:3\">HEB 1:1–1:3</a></p>\n<h3>He reveals God through his teaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:37\">JHN 18:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:28-Matt7:29\">MAT 7:28–7:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:11-John3:13\">JHN 3:11–3:13</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mission was to announce God's kingdom</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:17\">MAT 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:14-Mark1:15\">MRK 1:14–1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:28\">MAT 12:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:20\">LUK 11:20</a> <em>Jesus Christ's miracles reveal the presence of God's kingdom.</em></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mission was to redeem humanity</h2>\n<h3>He came to seek and save the lost</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:10\">LUK 19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:1-Luke15:10\">LUK 15:1–15:10</a></p>\n<h3>He came to save from sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:21\">MAT 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:25-Rom3:26\">ROM 3:25–3:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:15\">1TI 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>He came to break the devil's power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1JN 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:15\">GEN 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:31\">JHN 12:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14-Heb2:15\">HEB 2:14–2:15</a></p>\n<h3>He came to bring eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:10\">JHN 10:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:38-John6:40\">JHN 6:38–6:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:2-John17:3\">JHN 17:2–17:3</a></p>\n<h3>He came to give access to God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:18\">EPH 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:12\">EPH 3:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:19-Heb10:20\">HEB 10:19–10:20</a></p>\n<h3>He came to restore a fallen humanity</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:17-Rom5:18\">ROM 5:17–5:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:21-1Cor15:22\">1CO 15:21–15:22</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mission was to establish the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:18\">MAT 16:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:17-Eph2:19\">EPH 2:17–2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:25-Eph5:27\">EPH 5:25–5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:4-1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:4–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9-1Pet2:10\">1PE 2:9–2:10</a></p>\n<h2>The scope of Jesus Christ's mission</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ came first to Israel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:5-Matt10:6\">MAT 10:5–10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:24\">MAT 15:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:11\">JHN 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's mission extends to all peoples</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:6\">ISA 49:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:11\">MAT 8:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:16\">JHN 10:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:10\">MAT 8:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:9\">LUK 7:9</a> <em>Jesus Christ commends the faith of a Roman centurion</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:28\">MAT 15:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:29\">MRK 7:29</a> <em>Jesus Christ grants the request of a Canaanite woman</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a> <em>Jesus Christ sends his disciples out into the whole world</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:17-Acts26:18\">ACT 26:17–26:18</a> <em>Paul's commission to go to the Gentiles is received directly from Jesus Christ.</em></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mission made the cross necessary</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:28\">MAT 20:28</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:45\">MRK 10:45</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21\">MAT 16:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31\">MRK 8:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:50\">LUK 12:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:14-Col2:15\">COL 2:14–2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mission will be completed at his return</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:31\">MAT 24:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:27\">MRK 13:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:4\">COL 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:16-1Thess4:17\">1TH 4:16–4:17</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's mission continues through the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:21-John20:22\">JHN 20:21–20:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18-Matt28:20\">MAT 28:18–28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26-John15:27\">JHN 15:26–15:27</a></p>",
